Definition: social process of neutralizing the influence of Joseph Stalin by revising his policies and removing monuments dedicated to him and renaming places named in his honor
Example: his statue was demolished as part of destalinization
Synonyms: verb, change, destalinize, de-Stalinization, destalinisation, destalinise, de-Stalinisation, social_process, social, process, of, neutralizing, the, influence, Joseph, Stalin, by, revising, his, policies, and, removing, monuments, dedicated, to, him, renaming, places, named, in, honor, statue, was, demolished, as, part
Category: noun.process
